                    "@type": "Answer",
                    text: "FCA mandates oil meeting specification MS-12991, typically a 5W-40 synthetic. This low-ash oil is critical for protecting the turbocharger, timing chain, and preventing GPF clogging. Change intervals should not exceed 15,000 km or 1 year.",
