                    text: "The most frequent issues are variable intake manifold actuator failures, coolant leaks from the water pump, oil leaks from valve cover gaskets, and PCV system clogging. These are well-documented in FCA service bulletins, particularly SIB 09-015-20 for the intake manifold actuator.",
