                    "@type": "Answer",
                    text: "The FCA ZF engine is robust with excellent performance. Early models (2019-2020) had a noted 48V communication issue, addressed in MY2021 with revised hardware and software. With proper maintenance, use of 95 RON fuel, and correct oil (MS-12991), it can be very reliable long-term. The eTorque system adds complexity but is generally durable.",
