                    text: "The 552 63 113 is a powerful and torquey engine, but its long-term reliability is heavily dependent on maintenance. The high-pressure fuel pump is a known weak point. Vehicles with meticulous service records using the correct oil and high-quality diesel can be very reliable. Neglect, especially regarding fuel and oil quality, significantly increases the risk of costly failures.",
